  Fe 55.845 Fe_ONCV_PBE-1.2.upf
  H 1.00794 H_ONCV_PBE-1.2.upf
ATOMIC_POSITIONS crystal
  Fe 0.000000 0.000000 0.000000
  H 0.121910 0.878090 0.500000
  H 0.377895 0.622105 1.000000
  H 0.500000 0.500000 0.500000
  H 0.622105 0.377895 0.000000
  H 0.878090 0.121910 0.500000
K_POINTS automatic
  24 24 24 0 0 0
